{"tid":2279962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控721事件8個月活動 拳打追截青年警員 今被裁定罪名成立 判監30日","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T13:14:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e57e379d116ad5c74ec82685bc6638c3abf99c9","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11176&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=52ed9127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11176</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#王證瑜裁判官<br />\n#20200321元朗 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n曾(42)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲警<br />\n被控於2020年3月21日，在香港新界元朗鳳琴街18號玉龍樓地下7-11便利店外襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員，即督察18917李顯揚<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\n‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n‼️即時監禁30日‼️<br />\n<br />\n詳細後補"},{"pid":"f523391e3e3b52c43b4fcb5b86e75663b0003c29","tid":2279962,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"又老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448a12f61e3f7e92e9ea479479e4ffcab0674788","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ea7f389979fca5a2b07ee62955b96b74cad09c","tid":2279962,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"448a12f61e3f7e92e9ea479479e4ffcab0674788","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"30日係咪無得扣假"},{"pid":"460371449710f806928bef1435f08fc5a5094950","tid":2279962,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd0f79d90171aa06ab5d82e937150d0b1c4f3da","tid":2279962,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02ea7f389979fca5a2b07ee62955b96b74cad09c","tid":2279962,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"448a12f61e3f7e92e9ea479479e4ffcab0674788","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"30日係咪無得扣假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n <span class=\"red\">服刑中的囚犯如實際刑期超過1個月</span>，可因勤奮及行為良好而按照本條的規定獲得減刑<br />\n但本條並不准許將實際刑期減至少於31天。"},{"pid":"2f37fae809bd7a373256df8b6c2be2b960732aa8","tid":2279962,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967900155354bf10d4e2435a7cbe98176514772a","tid":2279962,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed85118d506520564ec31c2fc6e098242952ee5e","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"#屯門裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#王證瑜裁判官<br />\n#20200321元朗 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n曾(42)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲警<br />\n被控於2020年3月21日，在香港新界元朗鳳琴街18號玉龍樓地下7-11便利店外襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員，即督察18917李顯揚<br />\n<br />\n‼️簡短裁決理由‼️<br />\n是次案件有兩名控方證人，被告亦有作供，沒有辯方證人。<br />\n辯方提出幾個爭議點<br />\n1. PW1沒有合理理由懷疑被告干犯罪行<br />\n本席不同意，因為被告是從有非法集結的地方跑過來。<br />\n2. PW1使用過份武力 (發射胡椒噴霧)<br />\n本席不同意，因PW1看到有人靠近男子A，擔心有人搶犯才使用胡椒噴霧<br />\n3. 警員A對男子A使用過分武力，如發射胡椒噴霧及箍頸<br />\n本席不同意，從控方片段可看到發射胡椒噴霧的過程只有一秒，抱頭的過程只有三秒，只是為了制服男子A。<br />\n4. PW2在警誡方面的證供不可靠<br />\n本席考慮PW2就此方面的證供有不同版本，拒絕接納。<br />\n<br />\n但除了此部分的證供，PW1和PW2的其他證供合情合理，互相支持。<br />\n<br />\n本席不接納被告的證供。<br />\n1. 被告說他首先打到警員的頭盔，但片段中看到被告是打警員的背部。<br />\n2. 被告說他是為了阻止警員傷害男子A使用武力，引開他的注意力，因為他看見(2019年)8月31日警察向無辜市民使用武力。本席不接納此說法，因為當日的情況與8月31日的情況不同。如果被告想保護或拯救男子A，應該做出更直接的相關行為，例如將兩者分隔。片段中亦看到被告兩次向PW1施襲。被告聲稱想分散PW1的注意力，但PW1於第一次就襲後已轉身向被告，被告不必要進行第二次施襲。<br />\n3. 被告已知PW1當時正在執行職務，仍然主動去襲擊他，襲擊後立即跑走，與他想拯救男子A的意圖不符。<br />\n<br />\n因此裁定被告‼️罪名成立‼️。<br />\n<br />\n🌟求情🌟<br />\n被告孝順，為了母親的醫療及安葬費用而欠債，其後努力工作，已還了大部分債款。7月時發生了嚴重的家居意外，導致他腿部神經線及肌肉撕裂。呈上醫療報告及物理治療報告，報告顯示他只能步行一小時，只能行兩層樓梯，無法單腳企，到現時仍未完全康復，可以看到他到現在還是要戴腳托。現在他每星期都要做物理治療，如判處監禁式刑罰會影響他的康復進度。<br />\n<br />\n呈上幾封朋友的求情信，均指出被告樂於助人，見義勇為，為人正直。議員的求情信亦指他一直有幫忙做義工。案件中警察沒有受到重傷，亦沒有引起騷亂， 被告只是在千鈞一髮的情況下，用了非合法的方法助人... (裁判官：本席不接納這說法) ...作出了非合法的行為，希望法庭考慮監禁式刑罰會影響他的康復，以緩刑方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n‼️判刑‼️<br />\n裁判官指案情嚴重，因為被告在警員制服疑犯時襲擊兩次。然而考慮到他的動作不大，參考了他的醫療報告及求情信，以五個星期監禁為起點，但法庭留意到來被告腳傷的情況嚴重，本席同意如果要服刑，對他亦造成困難，因此減刑五天。但本席不同意被告傷勢嚴重至不能接受監禁，因此拒絕判處緩刑。本席宣判被告襲擊警務人員罪名成立，‼️即時監禁30天。‼️<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛#屯門裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#王證瑜裁判官<br />\n#20200321元朗 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n曾(42)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲警<br />\n被控於2020年3月21日，在香港新界元朗鳳琴街18號玉龍樓地下7-11便利店外襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員，即督察18917李顯揚<br />\n<br />\n‼️簡短裁決理由‼️<br />\n是次案件有兩名控方證人，被告亦有作供，沒有辯方證人。<br />\n辯方提出幾個爭議點<br />\n1. PW1沒有合理理由懷疑被告干犯罪行<br />\n本席不同意，因為被告是從有非法集結的地方跑過來。<br />\n2. PW1使用過份武力 (發射胡椒噴霧)<br />\n本席不同意，因PW1看到有人靠近男子A，擔心有人搶犯才使用胡椒噴霧<br />\n3. 警員A對男子A使用過分武力，如發射胡椒噴霧及箍頸<br />\n本席不同意，從控方片段可看到發射胡椒噴霧的過程只有一秒，抱頭的過程只有三秒，只是為了制服男子A。<br />\n4. PW2在警誡方面的證供不可靠<br />\n本席考慮PW2就此方面的證供有不同版本，拒絕接納。<br />\n<br />\n但除了此部分的證供，PW1和PW2的其他證供合情合理，互相支持。<br />\n<br />\n本席不接納被告的證供。<br />\n1. 被告說他首先打到警員的頭盔，但片段中看到被告是打警員的背部。<br />\n2. 被告說他是為了阻止警員傷害男子A使用武力，引開他的注意力，因為他看見(2019年)8月31日警察向無辜市民使用武力。本席不接納此說法，因為當日的情況與8月31日的情況不同。如果被告想保護或拯救男子A，應該做出更直接的相關行為，例如將兩者分隔。片段中亦看到被告兩次向PW1施襲。被告聲稱想分散PW1的注意力，但PW1於第一次就襲後已轉身向被告，被告不必要進行第二次施襲。<br />\n3. 被告已知PW1當時正在執行職務，仍然主動去襲擊他，襲擊後立即跑走，與他想拯救男子A的意圖不符。<br />\n<br />\n因此裁定被告‼️罪名成立‼️。<br />\n<br />\n🌟求情🌟<br />\n被告孝順，為了母親的醫療及安葬費用而欠債，其後努力工作，已還了大部分債款。7月時發生了嚴重的家居意外，導致他腿部神經線及肌肉撕裂。呈上醫療報告及物理治療報告，報告顯示他只能步行一小時，只能行兩層樓梯，無法單腳企，到現時仍未完全康復，可以看到他到現在還是要戴腳托。現在他每星期都要做物理治療，如判處監禁式刑罰會影響他的康復進度。<br />\n<br />\n呈上幾封朋友的求情信，均指出被告樂於助人，見義勇為，為人正直。議員的求情信亦指他一直有幫忙做義工。案件中警察沒有受到重傷，亦沒有引起騷亂， 被告只是在千鈞一髮的情況下，用了非合法的方法助人... (裁判官：本席不接納這說法) ...作出了非合法的行為，希望法庭考慮監禁式刑罰會影響他的康復，以緩刑方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n‼️判刑‼️<br />\n裁判官指案情嚴重，因為被告在警員制服疑犯時襲擊兩次。然而考慮到他的動作不大，參考了他的醫療報告及求情信，以五個星期監禁為起點，但法庭留意到來被告腳傷的情況嚴重，本席同意如果要服刑，對他亦造成困難，因此減刑五天。但本席不同意被告傷勢嚴重至不能接受監禁，因此拒絕判處緩刑。本席宣判被告襲擊警務人員罪名成立，‼️即時監禁30天。‼️<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"21518aa2dfd70e6593bcf0dde32907e397f8e64a","tid":2279962,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"王官不接納被告自辯時稱為保護及拯救年輕人、並且分散督察注意力的說法，認為事發當晚的情況與8.31無關兼且完全不同。若如被告所言，被告當時理應要求警方停止使用武力或分開雙方。而且督察在被告首次襲擊後已立即轉身，被告仍作第二襲擊，實屬無必要，與被告所指保護年輕人或分散督察注意力的說法不一致，裁定被告襲警罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/6MWJFX6T2VC6DJTUTYPGYQOGRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2F6MWJFX6T2VC6DJTUTYPGYQOGRQ%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=1a6ac7c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2F6MWJFX6T2VC6DJTUTYPGYQOGRQ%2F&h=7125baa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/6MWJFX6T2VC6DJTUTYPGYQOGRQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8cbe37e4b63397df3947cb5ef4e67c15bdaf4c8f","tid":2279962,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d161337dc0ed129c6bec981cb9068526dd8a6361","tid":2279962,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865fb00786f5f10aa0ae22a9d16fb583531f492e","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/localpresshk/18320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flocalpresshk%2F18320&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d1018da4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/localpresshk/18320</a><br />\n<br />\n//今年3.21 (元朗721 八個月)，41歲地盤工當日晚飯後途經元朗鳳琴街時，看見防暴警衝向1名年輕人，然後對其箍頸、揮棍和噴胡椒。<br />\n<br />\n地盤工庭上自辯時指當時看見警向年輕人揮警棍，才出手輕力打向黑警的頭盔，目的只是分散警注意力，不想年輕人受傷害。而庭上播放新聞片段，看到地盤工遭壓在地上，更被警瞄準眼睛噴胡椒。地盤工更投訴被捕後遭警棍毆打致身體多處受傷，須送院治療。<br />\n<br />\n今被控襲警罪成，判監30天。<br />\n<br />\n當日他可選擇視而不見，最後他的良知使他入獄，而罪名就是「不忍心看見年輕人受傷」。//"},{"pid":"67913c11e419f7f158a336c74599ee24e162d44a","tid":2279962,"uid":243677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"仆佢個臭街 721果班白衣人打人 就唔去捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a41898da088baa15f91a6da2e6df0a9c772b8d","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d161337dc0ed129c6bec981cb9068526dd8a6361","tid":2279962,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813e9b236f1f7d1481eae8faf37966cb00a49ad3","tid":2279962,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a41898da088baa15f91a6da2e6df0a9c772b8d","tid":2279962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d161337dc0ed129c6bec981cb9068526dd8a6361","tid":2279962,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e84c006a86f5cc22bc112364ca460b14250324","tid":2279962,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"被告自辯時稱，看見一名年輕人跑向他，同時防暴警員亦衝向他箍頸、施放胡椒噴霧。被告指該年輕人當時沒有暴力行為，但警員想攻擊他，令他想起 8.31 太子事件的新聞片段。他擔心防暴警員會傷害該年輕人，於是輕力打向警員頭盔，欲分散其注意力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%95%91%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-30-%E6%97%A5-%E5%AE%98%E6%8B%92%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%A8%B1-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%B3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2595%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-30-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=69f34e21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2595%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-30-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=785139c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%95%91%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-30-%E6%97%A5-%E5%AE%98%E6%8B%92%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%A8%B1-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%B3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"44df5237d24e4429c33e6f24f0c55de78d814747","tid":2279962,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba07da6aea401a75e4f093597a87d2ea3909a38e","tid":2279962,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}